title: Requires the state office of parks, recreation and historic preservation to evaluate, recommend and dedicate parcels of land in Onondaga county as parkland
summary: Requires the state office of parks, recreation and historic preservation to evaluate, recommend and dedicate parcels of land in Onondaga county as parkland; directs such office conduct an evaluation of vacant tracks of land for the purposes of increasing green spaces and developing trails to connect neighborhoods and towns.
actClause: AN ACT to require the state office of parks, recreation and historic preservation to evaluate, recommend and dedicate parcels of land located in Onondaga county as parkland
